original: Björklund, Knut Charles, tandläkare, Norrköping, f. 2/9/02 i Sthlm av Karl Gustaf B. o. Vivii Wadelius. G. 28 m. Elsa Kristina Ruus. Barn: Vivan f. 29, Kurt 30i, Marianne 32, Eva 33, Ulla 37, Karl Gunnar 40. — Stud:-ex. v. norra real i StiHm 22, tandl:-kand. 25, tandl. 27. Prakt, i Norrköp. sed. 27. Sekr. i Odontolog. fören. 26-27. Hobby: trädg : skötsel.
translated: Björklund, Knut Charles, dentist, Norrköping, b. 2/9/02 in Stockholm to Karl Gustaf B. and Vivii Wadelius. Married on 28/xx/yy to Elsa Kristina Ruus. Children: Vivan b. 1929, Kurt b. 1930, Marianne b. 1932, Eva b. 1933, Ulla b. 1937, Karl Gunnar b. 1940. — Graduated from Norra Real in Stockholm in 1922, studied dentistry and graduated in 1927. Has been practicing in Norrköping since 1927. Secretary for the Odontological Association in 1926-1927. Hobby: gardening.
